    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="[1-28th March 2021, Cox's Bazar] In affected camps (8E, 8W, 9) • Emergency repair interventions to damaged latrines and bathing shelters: replacement of slabs/satopan when needed, replacement of latrines superstructure with simple tarpauline/bamboo or wooden timbers. • Emergency hand washing stations to be installed in the proximity of latrines; recommended to have some daily workers to refill the handwashing stations and to provide soap (subsidized activity) &#10;In the camps affected by influx • Speed up the maintenance of existing latrines and bathing places • (if hosted HH will stay for long period in displacement) foresee increase of desludging activities."/>
